## Group Domain

# /domain/{domain}

## GET

This retrieves amounts of tokens for a domain as Json

+ Parameters
    + domain (string) - The domain
    
+ Response 200 (application/json)

    + Body

            {
              "status": "success",
              "result": 
                {
                  "confirmation": 1,
                  "pairs": 
                    [
                      {
                        "token": "AXNT",
                        "amount": "19.68043428"
                      },
                      {
                        "token": "EAGLE",
                        "amount": "0"
                      }
                    ]
                }
            }

        
## domain/transactions [GET /domain/{domain}/transactions{?page}{?per_page}{?direction}{?sort_field}{?actions}]

This retrieves the transactions for a domain as Json

+ Parameters
    + domain (string) - The domain
    + page: 0 (number, optional) - The page
    + per_page: 20 (number, optional) - The number of items per page
    + direction: up (string, optional) - The direction (up = ascending, down = descending)
    + sort_field: time (string, optional) - The sort field (id = transactionId, time = transaction timestamp)
    + actions (string, optional) - actions to filter in a comma delimited list e.g `?send,head`
    
+ Response 200 (application/json)

