## domain/amount/token [GET /domain/{domain}/token/{token}]

This retrieves the amount for a specified token for a domain as Json

+ Parameters
    + domain (string) - The domain
    + token (string) - The token
    
+ Response 200 (application/json)

    + Body

            {
              "status": "success",
              "result": 
                {
                  "confirmation": 1,
                  "pairs": 
                    [
                      {
                        "token": "AXNT",
                        "amount": "19.68043428"
                      }
                    ]
                }
            }